<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[الآد]</span>: القوة، قال <span class="c2">«١»</span>:<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>............... ... بأَدْمَاءَ تَنْهَضُ في آدِهَا<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
